The paper offers a formal definition of Artificial Intelligence, which is a core topic in the field of AI (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the algorithm for constructing AI, which falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also touches upon the role of knowledge in intelligence, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and robotics (cs.RO).
